outputs.output_descr: The project aims to contribute to ensuring and enhancing an effective and efficient health service delivery system in Eritrea. It will focus on supporting the MOH in strengthening its existing training centers and strengthening the capacity of the Monitoring and Evaluation Unit of the Ministry.

project_descr: The project support to improve the Intensive Care Unit (ICU) through the procurement of necessary equipment and strengthening capacity of the Ministry of Health to provide quality coverage of and access to health care services.
